@page "/project-8"

@layout HeaderLayout

<section class="project-cs-hero">
    <div class="project-cs-hero__content">
        <h1 class="heading-primary">MyAGC App</h1>
        <div class="project-cs-hero__info">
            <p class="text-primary">
                This page contains the case study of the MyAGC app which includes
                the Project Overview, Tools Used and Live Links to the official
                product.
            </p>
        </div>
        @*  <div class="project-cs-hero__cta">
        <a href="https://github.com/rammcodes/dopefolio" class="btn btn--bg" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Project
        Link</a>
        </div> *@
    </div>
</section>
<section class="project-details">
    <div class="main-container">
        <div class="project-details__content">
            <div class="project-details__showcase-img-cont">
                <img src="assets/png/MyAGC.png" alt="Project Image" class="project-details__showcase-img" />
            </div>
            <div class="project-details__content-main">
                <div class="project-details__desc">
                    <h2 class="project-details__content-title">Project Overview</h2>

                    <p class="project-details__desc-para">
                        MyAGC Application is a user-friendly platform designed to streamline the college admissions process for students across Africa. It allows undergraduate and postgraduate applicants to apply to multiple colleges, universities, and community colleges, provided that the institutions have open programs. 
                        The platform also supports consultants and licensed agents who can apply on behalf of students and earn commissions through a points-based system. Additionally, MyAGC features an online tracking module for users to send and receive goods, similar to Alibaba, making it a versatile tool for both education and logistics.
                    </p>
                    <p class="project-details__desc-para">
                        @*  I developed this project from April 2023 to August 2023. Since then,  *@I have been continuously enhancing it by adding new features and improving code readability through the implementation of various modern principles and best practices.
                    </p>
                    <p class="project-details__desc-para" style="color: red;">
                        Create your own account on the system <br />
                        <br />
                       
                    </p>

                    <p class="project-details__desc-para">
                        Feel free to check out the Project by visiting the <strong>Project Link</strong> below.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="project-details__tools-used">
                    <h2 class="project-details__content-title">Tools Used</h2>
                    <div class="skills">
                        <div class="skills__skill">HTML</div>
                        <div class="skills__skill">CSS</div>
                        <div class="skills__skill">JavaScript</div>
                        <div class="skills__skill">Bootstrap 5</div>
                        <div class="skills__skill">GIT</div>
                        <div class="skills__skill">Github</div>
                        <div class="skills__skill">C#</div>
                        <div class="skills__skill">SQL</div>
                        <div class="skills__skill">Paynow Integration</div>
                        <div class="skills__skill">.Net</div>
                        <div class="skills__skill">WebAPI (REST)</div>
                        <div class="skills__skill">Microsoft SQL Server</div>
                        <div class="skills__skill">SAP Crystal Reports</div>

                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="project-details__links">
                    <h2 class="project-details__content-title">See Live</h2>
                    <a href="https://tafadzwakahwai.ddns.net/MyAGC/login" class="btn btn--med btn--theme project-details__links-btn"
                       target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">System Link</a>
                    <a href="projects" class="btn btn--med btn--theme-inv project-details__links-btn">Go Back</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
